</item>
</list1>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM000000XH401BX_02" type-id="64" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___00007H300000">
<name>MONITOR DESCRIPTION</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A115898E03" width="7.106578999in" height="5.787629434in"/>
</figure>
<ptxt>If the ECM does not receive any IGF signals despite transmitting the IGT signal, it interprets this as a fault in the igniter and sets a DTC. </ptxt>
<ptxt>If the malfunction is not repaired successfully, a DTC is set 1 second after the engine is next started.</ptxt>
</content5>
</subpara>
